	* Source/NSTextView.m ([-moveWordBackward:]): Simplified.
	([-moveWordForward:]): Simplified.
	([-moveWordForwardAndModifySelection:]): New method, implemented.
	([-moveWordBackwardAndModifySelection:]): New method, implemented.
